    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip1a">Drag an image</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip1b"> onto this window or capture a screen region: TMHue extracts up to 15 dominant colors automatically.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip2a">All processing is </sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip2b">local</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip2c">: nothing is sent to the internet — your image never leaves your computer.</sys:String>
