    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip3b">copy</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip3c"> it in your default format.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip4a">Note:</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Palette.Tip4b"> when you close this window, the image and the extracted palette are discarded — nothing is saved.</sys:String>
